Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界因ZERO创造的奇迹而改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界因ZERO所展现的行动而重生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 当今世界正迈向新纪元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随着无数欲望与情感的波浪 ZERO必须前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是为了让时针继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和约定的一样 我一个人来了 到底怎么回事 杰雷米亚君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说皇女殿下的消息只能告诉我一个人

Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土之味

Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士团正朝着鹿儿岛沿岸前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是请大家放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我布里塔尼亚在Knight of One瓦尔德施泰因卿的指挥下…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里已是布里塔尼亚的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一兵一卒都别让他登陆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天英方向应该会薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让登陆部队咬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军朝着山口进发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加西亚队全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士团这些家伙 竟投入了这么多战力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想维持国土绝对防卫线 东中华海战却一直被星刻压着打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要惊慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要守住11区 以奥德修斯殿下为首的皇族都将入侵超合众国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其余的Knight of Rounds也将全体奔赴前线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要解放日本的话 布里塔尼亚的殖民地将一个个奋起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界地图将重新绘制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是天王山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经过去八年了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和娜娜莉被托付给这枢木神社
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 布里塔尼亚小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次遇见了朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救我想救的人 不需要什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前就是个不懂得变通的家伙 

Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是正因为如此 你成了我生平第一个朋友


Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 朱雀 我想赌在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如你能够接受我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够打啊 这种程度的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角突贯阵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最珍贵的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻大人 左翼崩坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一架突破能力超强的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让英迪拉队去援护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左翼全体保持后退 把那台机体孤立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:04:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈泽尔皇子应该还留在东京
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么可担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九州那边有帝国最强骑士Knight of One在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就留在东京 给他国一种“这只不过是场小纷争”的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗很快就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我没有判断错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在长崎出现的伏兵 被Grausam Valkyrie队消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向岛根派遣增援部队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面 也让莫利卿去援护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利姆卿后撤 和拉斯科卿汇合重新编队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的攻势看来快停了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔德施泰因大人出击的话 一口气解决他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了 以ZERO的作战而言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galahad出发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一特装使用援护装备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galahad出发!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你说好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚在特殊情况下 会设置31种路线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中对关系到皇族的线路尤其松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了 鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘亏你敢在我面前出现’
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是约定?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今谁还会相信你的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么也一个人来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不想再撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像对娜娜莉撒谎的你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直背叛着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对学生会的同伴 对娜娜莉也是 就连尤菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 藤堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的联络还没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Knight of Rounds都出现了 就算是星刻总司令也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能够相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自跟Orange、罗洛之流同伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得秘密太多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之前也秘密派遣木下他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO对目前的我们来说是必须的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是和扇他们说了很多次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 日本解放以后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇和迪特哈尔特去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想威胁我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁? 不不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想让你作为黑骑士团的一员 一如既往的工作而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望你不要妨碍ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 能代替我的人有一大把…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为你平凡 所以你的存在才有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织这种东西 成员各个都很耀眼是不能维持的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想确认一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有对尤菲使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让她屠杀日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我下令的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么下达这种GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让日本人奋起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本行政特区成立的话 黑骑士团就崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉之死呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说 夏莉和尤菲都只不过是实现野心的棋子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 所有的罪都在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这和娜娜莉无关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬出娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 哥哥为了我 一直扮演着圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的哥哥的外表和ZERO的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个才是真正的鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 连这里都没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀没来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把洪古的部队投入左翼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备第二次突击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下是指挥官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擒王来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是战术的基本…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝亲自命名的圣剑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我生平第一次向人低头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾不得体面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外我别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算GEASS也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 救救娜娜莉吧 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今…你这算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你会被原谅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在我只能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救娜娜莉 只有靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当我会原谅你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会原谅你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你骗的人 因你而死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今知道认错的话 就把尤菲给我复活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的恶意挽救世界给我看看 现在立刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是创造奇迹的ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是计算和演出的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称为ZERO的假面只是记号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是为了撒谎而制造的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么装置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这种藉口能说得过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是谎言的话 就给我圆谎到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是过去不会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么给我下了“活下去”的GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么




Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我下的“活下去”的GEASS 扭曲了我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对我下那样的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因涉嫌暗杀克洛维斯殿下而被问罪 你为什么要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了获取日本人的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒店劫持事件 营救学生会成员又是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想利用它让黑骑士团亮相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这眼神…我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是隐藏秘密接受惩罚的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我加入了布里塔尼亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了补偿 为了不让悲剧重演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谎言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修 有一个补偿你谎言的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是让你的谎言成真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谎称你是正义的伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就成为真正的正义的伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把谎言撒到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束这场战争 如果你是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是只有ZERO才能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用让世界变得和平 大家变得幸福的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话 我就把娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了娜娜莉 再一次与你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的话 无论什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经知道你的真面目了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 枢木卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从一开始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你立下大功了 枢木卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样战争就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你又打算出卖我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背叛我 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背叛了我!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近朱雀的样子有点奇怪 就觉得他是不是有所松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在学生会室发现的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当成宝贝似的放在储物柜里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多地方都被撕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你… 和恐怖份子关系融洽的情形也许不太好留下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 大家一起么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会流露出这样的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没见过朱雀像这样的笑过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是布里塔尼亚人和11区人的混血儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃红月 选择斯坦菲尔德这名字的话 就可以很好的生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有这种想法的话 想成为Knight of Rounds也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想问你有没有回来这边的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布兰德利卿 请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打成这样 反正是要沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就让卢西亚诺来有效利用一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气解决
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用同伴的舰艇来做武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持炮击 全速后退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有两下子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 在这个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 挺身吃我一剑衔接随后的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻此人 被称为麒麟儿看来并非浪得虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻总司令好像负伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大龙胆 后退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战指挥转移给参谋长周香凛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到时候吗 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的真面目居然真的是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇族杀手ZERO的真面目居然是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何等的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 鲁鲁修 皇帝陛下那边由我来周旋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 责罚是不可避免 你的性命我或许还能保住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怜悯我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 全部是修奈泽尔殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是跟着你就能找到ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下已经察觉到了 你和ZERO不寻常的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修 就算是现在我也想扮演你哥哥的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会害你 能信任我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任你?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 信任你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遗憾 皇兄 我已经不再相信任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的友情被出卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人 你不是Orange
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我只是想拜托你点事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 要我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 很简单的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我摆出这个姿势 那一刻你就把我当作科奈莉娅 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的骑士吉尔弗德 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你注意到了 吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔弗德卿 你这是干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们才是 居然逮捕皇女 发疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连吉尔弗德卿也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只有相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇女殿下 暂且先离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 我最初也是最后的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直无法相信 吉尔弗德卿居然会叛变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里待机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 修奈泽尔殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说ZERO出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也没被通知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像得知什么非常糟糕的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想确认一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有对尤菲使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的话 应该清楚吉尔弗德卿叛变的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及你曾经在神根岛采取的行动的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是应该追击ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们缺少非常重要的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所知道的情报…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wired-C 确认反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ragnarok Backup 进行复位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔弗德 就这样前往东京租界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名誉布里塔尼亚人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knight of Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是枢木玄武首相的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修的朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米娅的骑士?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意说的话 我们就只有投身不公平的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让这悲哀的连锁持续到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租界结构的修改已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会像以前那样让ZERO破坏这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到了 是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Vincent打下来也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为我在租界就只是当个学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京租界 现在就让你停止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Energy Filler…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gefion Disturber吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 关于这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视机前的各位观众 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放室的电源好像断了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 条件就绪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七号作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑鸠浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑鸠浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队各战斗部队 随时准备浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰队就这样穿过东京湾 突入东京租界 和ZERO会合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各员 战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的忠义 为了鲁鲁修殿下和娜娜莉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 黑骑士团突入东京湾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔德施泰因卿 派我和直属的Grausam Valkyrie队去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去东京租界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想建功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是想破坏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛 你那如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 作战已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去迎接娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 拜托了 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情什么的是靠不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 无情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不将自我化为完全体 就不能把娜娜莉夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修 从克洛维斯那时我就觉得事有蹊跷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我已经理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解并接受了 现在所有的牌都在我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 一开始就告诉修奈泽尔殿下的话 就不会引发这样的战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Knight of Rounds 我不能处罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理的罪恶就自己去寻找答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界不会只对你一个人温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有坐上去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上这装着Freyja的Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Freyja把鲁鲁修…

Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你真敢干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,欺骗我 践踏我的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,鄙视我的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我会赢过修奈泽尔 朱雀给你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们把我设为目标而行动着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 来迎接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:23:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来破坏 让我给你们看看绝望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我再去迎接娜娜莉 解救卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,最后笑的会是我
